snippet: Mr. Sanders cut into Mrs. Clinton’s lead by more than two dozen delegates, but his mathematical chances of winning the nomination have not improved.
abstract: Sen Bernie Sanders scores victory in Washington State's Democratic primary, while Hillary Clinton wins Guam caucuses.
lead_paragraph: Mr. Sanders cut into Mrs. Clinton’s lead by more than two dozen delegates, but his mathematical chances of winning the nomination have not improved.

headline.main: Bernie Sanders Picks Up Washington Delegates; Hillary Clinton Wins Guam
headline.print_headline: Sanders Picks Up Washington State Delegates; Clinton Wins Guam
